msgctxt "search_description"
msgid "The essays will be used to help expand Mozilla’s Common Voice Kiswahili open-source data set, enabling the inclusion of local African languages in tech use and development."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "body.31c2090a-3b86-4888-aea8-1472edb19097.altText"
msgid "An image of a seated man using a laptop to access Common Voice platform"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "body.529bf6f3-d89f-43f7-8074-824d25b402af"
msgid ""
"Once again Mozilla’s Common Voice and Hekaya Arts initiative are calling upon Kiswahili writers to submit creative essays in fiction and non-fiction subcategories. (Our <a id=\"a1\">last "
"competition</a> was in April 2022.) The winning prizes for the top three best essays are USD $400, $250, and $100 respectively."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "body.529bf6f3-d89f-43f7-8074-824d25b402af"
msgid ""
"Writers are encouraged to stretch their creativity and language prowess, including writing in various Kiswahili dialects. The reviewing panel also welcomes submissions of translated works given that"
" the original author(s) are credited."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "body.529bf6f3-d89f-43f7-8074-824d25b402af"
msgid "The essays will be used to help expand Mozilla’s Common Voice <a id=\"a1\">Kiswahili open-source data set</a>, enabling the inclusion of local African languages in tech use and development."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "body.529bf6f3-d89f-43f7-8074-824d25b402af"
msgid "Entries should be submitted <a id=\"a1\">here</a>; and the deadline is Friday, September 30, 2022. Winners will be announced and awarded before the end of October."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "body.529bf6f3-d89f-43f7-8074-824d25b402af"
msgid "Submission Guidelines"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "body.529bf6f3-d89f-43f7-8074-824d25b402af"
msgid "Received submissions will be in the public domain. All work submitted will be under Public Domain (CC-0) license."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "body.529bf6f3-d89f-43f7-8074-824d25b402af"
msgid "Submissions should be between 2,500 to 5,000 words."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "body.529bf6f3-d89f-43f7-8074-824d25b402af"
msgid "Text specifications"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "body.529bf6f3-d89f-43f7-8074-824d25b402af"
msgid "There should be no digits in the written work such as 2021; instead, use words."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "body.529bf6f3-d89f-43f7-8074-824d25b402af"
msgid "Abbreviations and acronyms like “USA” or “ICE” should be avoided because they may be read in a way that does not coincide with their spelling"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "body.529bf6f3-d89f-43f7-8074-824d25b402af"
msgid "The text should not use derogatory language"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "body.529bf6f3-d89f-43f7-8074-824d25b402af"
msgid "The text should not promote any form of gender harassment, abuse, or violence"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "body.529bf6f3-d89f-43f7-8074-824d25b402af"
msgid "The text should not perpetuate or condone sexual harassment or biases"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "body.529bf6f3-d89f-43f7-8074-824d25b402af"
msgid "The text should be respectful of gender diversities i.e. usage of correct pronouns"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "body.529bf6f3-d89f-43f7-8074-824d25b402af"
msgid "The text should not propagate violence and/or threats of violence"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "body.529bf6f3-d89f-43f7-8074-824d25b402af"
msgid "The text should be in a digital format not handwritten"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "body.529bf6f3-d89f-43f7-8074-824d25b402af"
msgid "The content must be your own, no plagiarized content"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "body.529bf6f3-d89f-43f7-8074-824d25b402af"
msgid "Remember, content that will be viewed as offensive in any way will be declined"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "title"
msgid "Open Call: The Second Edition of Common Voice’s Kiswahili Essay Writing Competition"
msgstr ""
